title: Vegetable Stew
content:
Vegetable Stew is a category of item. It can be cooked in The Delectable Dab Kitchen in Hopeport using the Chef profession. Recipes for the Chef profession can be found in the Chef Recipe Book. Vegetable Stews can be sold to Head Chef.


 * Basic Vegetable Stew
 * Appetizing Vegetable Stew
 * Fine Vegetable Stew
 * Tasty Vegetable Stew
 * Delicious Vegetable Stew
 * Gourmet Vegetable Stew
